ce:section.ce:para:
In order to assess the biocompatibility of COFBDP/CD-S-3 and COFBDP/CD-S-3-Ag, a hemolysis assay was performed using defibrillated sheep blood. The results of the experiment demonstrated that when the concentration of COFBDP/CD-S-3-Ag and COFBDP/CD-S-3 was maintained at ≤ 200 μg mL−1, the hemolysis rate was below 5%, indicating that both COFBDP/CD-S-3-Ag and COFBDP/CD-S-3 are biocompatible (Fig. 6
                         and Table 4
                        )
